room_title: Escape room "Elf Academy" by Escape Reality Games in Sarasota
room_address: 6250 N Lockwood Ridge Rd Sarasota, FL 34243
room_description: You've been training for this holly jolly moment all your life, baking cookies, singing Christmas carols, wrapping presents, trying to find out who's naughty and nice... Now you've got 60 minutes to prove you know Christmas inside and out and join the ranks of the Elf Team! Can you pass Santa's final exam?
